      "pol": "pol_neutral"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "BJe2djKE3X",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "text": "#9) I think that MNIST is almost a toy experiment, since the crucial component of the proposed method is the prior modeling with the GAN.",
